            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">為配合即將上映的 《死侍與狼人》，Microsoft 與 Marvel Studios 合作推出一款全新 Xbox 無線手掣。上週推出的 Xbox Cheeky 手掣以死侍圓潤臀部為設計靈感，今次輪到狼人，以其「Hugh Jackman 合金臀部」成為手掣賣點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252092 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controller_wv-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controller_wv-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controller_wv.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新 Xbox 手掣最大賣點在於以影星 Hugh Jackman 的合金臀部（圖片來源：<a href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2024/07/22/deadpool-wolverine-xbox-controller-wolverine-design/">Xbox</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">新 Xbox 手掣最大賣點在於其誇張後部設計，以影星 Hugh Jackman 的合金臀部作藍本。目前尚未清楚新設計下如何存取電池，但手掣其他功能與標準版無異。手掣設計融合狼人在電影中穿著的標誌性黃色戰衣，從質感、顏色到側邊藍色細節都一一呈現。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1252107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controllerdp_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controllerdp_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controllerdp_.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">狼人手掣與死侍手掣一樣，並不會公開發售。用家想要擁有它，唯一方法是參加微軟在 Instagram 上舉辦的抽獎活動。首先要追蹤微軟 Xbox Instagram 帳號，按讚抽獎貼文，再留言標註三位朋友方有機會獲得。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1252108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/billboardlandscapea9-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/billboardlandscapea9-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/billboardlandscapea9.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2024/07/22/deadpool-wolverine-xbox-controller-wolverine-design/">Xbox</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/senuas-saga-hellblade-ii-review/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】《Senua&#8217;s Saga: Hellblade II》 精神病主題黑暗風格</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/xbox-boss-i-think-we-should-have-a-handheld-too/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Xbox 主管暗示有意開發手提遊戲機　對 Steam Deck 等遊戲機很有好感</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/12/microsoft-says-it-needs-games-like-hi-fi-rush-the-day-after-killing-its-studio/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Microsoft 關閉旗下多間遊戲工作室　強調需要製作「小型但有影響力的遊戲」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/hugh-jackman-xbox/game-channel/">微軟《死侍與狼人》 Xbox 手掣，狼人也有份 + 背面「合金臀部」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
